{"tid":2442622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"福原愛不能認出軌！日媒爆她「想進軍中國」：有瑕疵恐出局","createTime":"2021-03-11T12:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T03:39:06.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6299ea6c42ea14a1384d68c11894c425bc34ac12","tid":2442622,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"台日桌球夫婦江宏傑、福原愛的婚變疑雲，持續延燒，福原愛被拍到與一名高大男子同遊<br />\n橫濱，還一同過夜，不過福原愛多次聲明，自己並沒有外遇，否認不倫。對此，日本媒體<br />\n《東京體育》（東スポ）今（11）日報導指出，福原愛未來可能到中國大陸發展，由於中<br />\n國對於公眾人物規範要求很高，如果涉及醜聞，恐怕會失去阻斷這條路的發展。<br />\n <br />\n福原愛被日本知名周刊《女性SEVEN》拍到和一名高大男性出遊橫濱，甚至還被爆同進同<br />\n出飯店。對此，福原愛駁斥外遇傳聞，表示是一人一間，這名男性朋友是在6、7年前飯局<br />\n認識的，後來就沒有再聯絡，一直到她今年回日本，因為壓力大、心情不好，才決定主動<br />\n聯絡他，更稱對方給她精神上的支持。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://pse.is/3dn9v9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2F3dn9v9&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=62585cb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://pse.is/3dn9v9</a>"},{"pid":"05dfb7c0fcf7752ea384e32b1097d2e4e3b9bdfd","tid":2442622,"uid":190970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:47:45.000Z","msg":"去做雞？"},{"pid":"f5f24696c36ac7e2240ff204cb56bd3524f0834a","tid":2442622,"uid":299694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e92c0b1e98ed5646429e9186653a3da4359276","tid":2442622,"uid":119828,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"暴絲狂狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3356374cfe13d1f20f6a32a57719f46d1401c2d0","tid":2442622,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05dfb7c0fcf7752ea384e32b1097d2e4e3b9bdfd","tid":2442622,"uid":190970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12: